    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Finnamus atque largimus
                        nos domnus <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/158" key="#Marquis/duke #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">Gisolfus</persName> summus
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> gentis Langobardorum, vobis <persName key="#Abbesses" ref="#people/1934"
                            >Gausani</persName> dicate Deo <rs key="#Abbesses">abbatisse</rs> et
                            <persName key="#Nuns/sanctimoniales"><name ref="Pancrituda"
                                >Pancricude</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Nuns/sanctimoniales"><name ref="Gariperga"
                            >Gariperge</name></persName>
                        <rs key="Nuns/sanctimoniales">religiosissime ancille Christi</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Abbesses #Nuns/sanctimoniales"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/97">Sancte Marie</orgName> in <placeName
                            key="#Monasteries #Abbesses #Nuns/sanctimoniales" ref="#places/193"
                            >Cingla</placeName>. Quia manifesta causa est, quoniam postposuistis
                        parentes et substantias vestras et venistis peregrinare in terra nostra
                        Beneventana, et nos propter Deum et anime nostre mercedem et quia post Deum
                        in nostra venistis fiducia, dedimus vobis una cum beatissimo patre nostro
                            <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/2923">Petronaci</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> cella in Cingla, quȩ pertinet de iure <orgName key="#Abbots"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti Benedicti</orgName>, et una cum ipso
                        vobis suprascriptum monasterium tradere fecimus et substantiam largiti sumus
                        una cum <persName ref="#people/2002" key="#Marquis/duke"
                            >Scauneperga</persName> gloriosa coniuge nostra. Unde previdimus vos
                        suprascriptas in ipso sancta cenobio confirmare in eo ordine, ut dum una ex
                        vobis advixerit, inibi regimen tenere debeatis, ut super vos alia priore non
                        imponatur, quia et ex parte ibidem noster est labor; nam post vero vestro
                        discessu quorum supra, quem ipsa sancta congregatio elegerit et providerit,
                        potestas de abbate, qui fuerit Sancti Benedicti, ipsa confirmetur, nam dum
                        vos vixeritis, in vestra sit potestate secundum honorem et conversationem
                        vestram, si recte et caste vixenus atque conversavenus. Quod enim preceptum
                        largitati seu firmitatis ex iussione suprascripti domni viri gloriosissimi
                        Gisolfi et ex dictato <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Scarolfus"
                                >Scarolfi</name></persName> notarii scripsi ego <persName
                            key="#Notary"><name ref="Beatus">Beatus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Data iussione in hunc sacratissimo
                            <placeName key="#Palatium" ref="#places/110">Beneventano</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Palatium">palatio</rs>, mense Magio, per indictione quintadecima;
                        feliciter.</ab>
